OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779797464
OL,3,CRoyal International Air Tattoo 2026
OL,4,Ccancelled amid Middle East war
OL,6,FThis year's Royal International Air
OL,7,FTattoo has been cancelled because of
OL,8,Fongoing operations at RAF Fairford.
OL,10,FThe airshow has been held at the base
OL,11,Fin Gloucestershire since 1985,
OL,12,Fbecoming an annual show in 1993, and
OL,13,Fwelcomes aircraft from around the
OL,14,Fworld for displays and demonstrations.
OL,16,FIt celebrated its 50th anniversary
OL,17,Flast year, attracting crowds of more
OL,18,Fthan 170,000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
