OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779797464
OL,3,CRoyal International Air Tattoo 2026
OL,4,Ccancelled amid Middle East war
OL,6,FEarlier this year saw the arrival of
OL,7,Fdozens of US bombers at RAF Fairford
OL,8,Fwhich is being used as a base of
OL,9,Foperations in the war in Iran.
OL,11,FConcerns about access to the airbase
OL,12,Fhave now prompted organisers of the
OL,13,Fairshow to cancel the event, which was
OL,14,Fdue to take place in July.
OL,16,FIn a statement, organisers announced
OL,17,Fthe news "with great disappointment."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779797464
OL,3,CRoyal International Air Tattoo 2026
OL,4,Ccancelled amid Middle East war
OL,6,FThey said: "We understand how much
OL,7,FRIAT means to so many people; our
OL,8,Fvisitors, volunteers, partners, and
OL,9,Fthe wider community who return year
OL,10,Fafter year. We know the memories,
OL,11,Ftraditions, and anticipation that
OL,12,Fbuild around the event.
OL,14,F"This has not been an easy decision.
OL,15,FIt follows extensive discussions with
OL,16,Fthe Royal Air Force and the United
OL,17,FStates Air Force regarding uncertainty
OL,18,Fover access to RAF Fairford, given the
OL,19,Fongoing situation in the Middle East.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1779797464
OL,3,CRoyal International Air Tattoo 2026
OL,4,Ccancelled amid Middle East war
OL,6,F"Anyone who has already purchased a
OL,7,Fticket for this year's show will be
OL,8,Foffered the choice to roll their
OL,9,Fticket over to next year, donate the
OL,10,Fcost to charity or receive a full
OL,11,Frefund.
OL,13,FGavin Gager, Chief Executive Officer
OL,14,Fof Royal Air Force Charitable Trust
OL,15,FEnterprises, says he knows "how
OL,16,Fdisappointing this news will be."
OL,26,@wD@\OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
